summary: Now takin' bets, who's gonna get wrekt? ------------------------------------------------------- feels bad leaving this blank so...
caption:
Now takin’ bets, who’s gonna get wrekt?

——————————————————-

feels bad leaving this blank so here’s Goob trivia


-If Goober was a real dog he would be a teacup corgi that unfortunately stayed small in body but not so much in ears
-Goober has lineage bred moves from Set and his mom’s parents like Cross Chop, Blaze Kick/High Jump Kick and Bullet Punch. He’s not big enough to use them despite being there so he has placeholder moves like Force Palm, Low Kick and Laser Focus
-Goober and Set both have chow tongues but its easier to see on Set cause he has more tongue to see

Welcome!  I create, using the all-mighty classic Microsoft XP Paint, my own pokemon fusions. All the sprites come from pokestadium and usually people on deviantart/ the xy/sun&moon sprite project. I don't own any of the sprite used, I just fuse them! 
REQUESTS ARE OPEN! Ask Box: 3/15.
PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DRAW MY FUSIONS!!  I absolutely love it when people draw them! There's no need to ask either! Just make sure you tag me so them I can see it!
I hope you enjoy my fusions!

summary: Whimxen Whimsicott and Braixen fusion Fairy/Fire Type Ability: Infiltrator/Fluffy The Fluff Covered Pokemon Whimxen look cute...
caption:
Whimxen

Whimsicott and Braixen fusion

Fairy/Fire Type

Ability: Infiltrator/Fluffy

The Fluff Covered Pokemon

Whimxen look cute but they can be rather scary when hungry.  Its fluff is very similar to Mareep’s wool and many farmers will keep Whimxen around to help keep Mareep safe from predators.  Sometimes, it will use fire type attacks and singe the ends off of its fluff.

Request for @crystal-pancakes. I hope you like it! I wanted to bring out the fairy type in whimsicott as you wanted a fairy theme going on.
